            "title": "長城汽車去年多賺近81%  派息增50%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長城汽車(02333)公布，去年盈利126.92億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增長80.76%。派末期息每股0.45元，較上年度0.3元增50%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：長城汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230726_FI_source-web_02333.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：長城汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230726_FI_source-web_02333.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：長城汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">扣除非經常損益淨利97.35億元，按年升101.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">營業總收入2021.95億元，按年升17.73%。銷量微升0.37%至約123.5萬部，當中，出口急升近45%至45.4萬部；產量跌近4%至120.8萬部。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率19.51%，按年上升1.36個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">經營活動金流淨額2778.26億元，按年升56.49%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14813822-%e9%95%b7%e5%9f%8e%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e5%a4%9a%e8%b3%ba%e8%bf%9181-%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e50",
