            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價再創新高，美國關稅措施引發全球貿易戰擔憂，資金流向黃金避險。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"金價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20170226_FI_Gold_FB_source-web_-4-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"金價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20170226_FI_Gold_FB_source-web_-4-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">金價 (Shutterstock圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金高見每盎司3086.7美元，升幅1%，較早時徘徊3084美元附近。全星期計，連升4星期。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期金升穿3100美元關口，高見3124.4美元，收報3114.3美元，升23.4美元，升幅約0.8%；本周累計升3.1%。</p>\n</div>",
